These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, journalist
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the architect and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | architect | analyst   | journalist |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike | car        |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, tea
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, turtle
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | tea | cola   | soy-milk   |
| Pet        | rat | turtle | chinchilla |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, strawberry
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, subway
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person driving the bus##7
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | nectarine | strawberry | cauliflower |
| Transport   | bus       | subway     | car         |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, zombie
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | adventure | horror    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, time-travel
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel | adventure |
| Pet           | horse    | turtle      | hedgehog  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
