3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
4. the photographer is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | photographer | dancer | security-guard |
| Pet   | horse        | goat   | chinchilla     |

