.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, pilot, writer
1. the pilot is between the writer and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the writer##8
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the writer##8
4. the writer is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | sprite |
| Job        | writer      | pilot    | lawyer |

