3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
4. the egyptian is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | turkish | dutch    | egyptian |
| Sport         | skiing  | climbing | swimming |

