.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, raspberry, watermelon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance
1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person eating pear##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | pear  | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | drama | romance   |

