.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, skydiving
1. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person drinking iced-tea##7
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | juice     | sprite | iced-tea   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | hiking | card-games |

