2. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
3. the fan of house is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | electronic | house |
| Nationality   | brazilian | thai       | dutch |

