.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, house
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, tennis
1. the fan of house is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of house is between the fan of electronic and the fan of d&b##2
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | house      | electronic |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | tennis     |

