3 different pets are kept: fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is not the person eating apricot##6
2. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
4. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | orange | raspberry | apricot    |
| Pet    | goat   | fish      | guinea-pig |

