.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, video-games
There are 3 different nationalities: american, brazilian, indonesian
1. the brazilian is somewhere between the indonesian and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
2. the american is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
3. the american is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | brazilian    | american    |

